llm_response: There are 219 projects that match your criteria. All projects are in the Health sector. Projects are located in: .

metadata.sql_query:
SELECT 
    projectname as project_name,
    district,
    projectsector as project_sector,
    projectstatus as project_status,
    COALESCE(budget, 0) as total_budget,
    COALESCE(completionpercentage, 0) as completion_percentage
FROM proj_dashboard 
WHERE LOWER(projectsector) LIKE '%health%';
